cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with physical layer security in a wireless communication network, which involves information theory (cs.IT), cryptography and security (cs.CR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves multiple antennas and maximal-ratio combining. However, given the focus on security and wireless communication, cs.IT and cs.CR are the most likely categories.
